description: A National Security Council spokesperson said, “The United States will stand with the people of Israel and support their defense against these threats from Iran."
title: Biden Will Meet With National Security Team as U.S. Pledges ‘Support’ for Israel Against Iran

description: Iran launched drones toward Israel Saturday, the Israeli military announced.
title: Israel Says Iran Has Launched a Number of Drones Toward It and Closes Its Airspace

description: The Israeli military said dozens of people, Palestinians and Israelis, were injured in confrontations in several locations Saturday.
title: West Bank Sees Some of Its Worst Violence Since War in Gaza Began as Israeli Teen’s Body Is Found

description: 174 people stranded in cable cars above a mountain in Turkey were brought to safety Saturday, nearly 23 hours after one pod hit a pole and burst open.
title: 174 People Stranded in the Air Are Rescued After Fatal Cable Car Accident in Turkey

description: Iran's Revolutionary Guard seized an Israeli-affiliated container ship near the Strait of Hormuz, the latest in a series of attacks between the two countries.
title: Iran’s Revolutionary Guard Seizes Container Ship Near Strait of Hormuz Amid Tensions With West

description: A man stabbed six people to death at a busy Sydney shopping center Saturday before he was fatally shot, police said.
title: Six People Stabbed to Death in Sydney Shopping Center, Suspect Fatally Shot

description: Welcome to the age of “Dating People When You Hate People,” writes Myisha Battle.
title: If You’re Dating Right Now, You’re Brave
